title: 153: Senior Bowl practice, Conference Championship recap
itunes:title: 153: Senior Bowl practice, Conference Championship recap
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are in Mobile, Alabama scouting the talent at the Senior Bowl. The duo weighs in on what they’ve seen in practice so far and DJ talks to Eastern Washington wide receiver Cooper Kupp. DJ and Bucky also recap the AFC and NFC Conference Championships as the Falcons and Patriots advanced to Super Bowl LI.
